Bobik,is,a,web,service,for,scraping,websites,in,real,time,Bobik,allows,users,to,collect,and,retrieve,information,from,websites,automatically,and,in,real,time,The,Bobik,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Bobik,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,creating,and,setting,scraping,jobs,managing,account,information,and,retrieving,scrapes